<item>
            <title>[LU-4556] speed up sanity-lfsck and sanity-scrub tests</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4556</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The test time of sanity-scrub and sanity-lfsck is much longer than it needs to be, especially in DNE mode, because it is reformatting all of the OSTs and MDTs for every test, and then repopulating the filesystem with test files.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It would be better to avoid reformatting the filesystems at all, and instead just compare the &quot;new&quot; results with the &quot;old&quot; results.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;There may be other potential areas of improvement also.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
